<!--T:5-->
===Inventory===
''See also [[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory|Inventory]] for more detailed information.''

<!--T:6-->
VRC+ subscribers can upload and manage custom content types in their inventory, including user icons, photos, custom emojis, custom stickers, and prints. Users can create them by using the in-client [[Camera]], or through the VRChat website.
